      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Turns out I was wrong specifically about Apache HTTP client being pulled in automatically... my apologies. Spring will use it if it is on the classpath, but otherwise fallback to HttpUrlConnection. But in any case, specifying versionless should always be preferred for dependencies managed by Spring Boot (and Apache HTTP client is)"
