    "body" : "<p>The solution is replace</p>\n<pre><code>implementation(&quot;org.apache.httpcomponents:httpclient:4.5.14&quot;)\n</code></pre>\n<p>with</p>\n<pre><code>Implementation(&quot;org.apache.httpcomponents.client5:httpclient5&quot;)\n</code></pre>\n"
